m/"}, "format": "dash-1279636920730938v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by michaelrothman", "description": "Just another thoughtful and heartfelt message from James Van Der Beek from a few years back. He really was always pensive and sharing some helpful insight into the world and spirituality #jamesvanderbeek #dawsonscreek", "duration": 75.333, "timestamp": 1771174007, "uploader_id": "5687631388", "uploader": "Michael Rothman", "channel": "michaelrothman", "like_count": 6498, "comment_count": 132, "comments": [{"author": "doctorzorz", "author_id": "2070083604", "id": "18378945961089795", "text": "What a wonderful dude. So grateful I been following him last few years.", "timestamp": 1771339966}, {"author": "neon.attitude", "author_id": "3560792464", "id": "18338287216244673", "text": "Beautiful man.", "timestamp": 1771303343}, {"author": "sunshine2532", "author_id": "309430693", "id": "17942612817131628", "text": "My heart…💔", "timestamp": 1771278387}, {"author": "francavalenti2", "author_id": "24097308784", "id": "18103739641829428", "text": "Una saggezza immensa, competente su tutto, preparato in ogni campo, tutto ciò che faceva gli riusciva bene, ballare, cantare,recitare....ma soprattutto amare ed essere un padre fantastico! Mancherai al mondo James 💔😢", "timestamp": 1771265216}, {"author": "curiouscreaturesphotography", "author_id": "1308832489", "id": "18058659020357307", "text": "A beautiful and simple perspective so gently given ❤️", "timestamp": 1771259359}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/632954500_903782885889882_8967208764024167716_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4LmRlZmF1bHRfY292ZXJfZnJhbWUuYzIifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=106&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gH1Pf0kIO9HK-3RB8sNZ6eYP4qbUDonJMCDTB6kjA0_7yzNZFtBBeDtTRP3TKlj8BE&_nc_ohc=mF1hGwLd9DYQ7kNvwHMXSFB&_nc_gid=tPz1O1MpG_hxePQojdFnGw&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af21JPFPDN-Tov